{"tid":2187572,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"UBER你幾時先肯死心","createTime":"2020-09-03T16:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T09:00:13.000Z","uid":239696,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d0550d69b1bd255b3bdf18d590c96be3540cd39e","tid":2187572,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"行政長官現正就本年度施政報告展開公眾諮詢，我們懇請你發表意見，表達你對立法規管汽車共乘服務的支持。<br />\n<br />\n六年來，香港政府仍未願意與 Uber 會面，探討點對點交通服務在香港的未來發展。你的支持對我們非常重要，故我們再次向各位發送這封電郵，希望你能為 Uber 提供支持和幫助。<br />\n<br />\n終審法院最近的判決使我們感到非常失望，並對點對點交通行業的發展造成影響。香港一直對汽車共乘服務持續欠缺明確法規，再加上最近的裁決，影響超過 14,000 名 Uber 活躍司機夥伴於當前經濟危機依賴 Uber 維持日常生計，更影響數百萬使用 Uber 服務代步的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n在欠缺明確法規的情況下，Uber 無法為香港帶來更多投資及就業機會。<br />\n<br />\n因此我們再次懇請你在施政報告公眾諮詢期間，表達你對立法規管汽車共乘服務的支持，讓香港政府聽到你的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n最後，衷心感謝你一路上對 Uber 的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然我成鳩日用你，但都咁撚多年啦，你都仲未明香港政府根本唔需要創新，只需要保住而家班既得利益者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢唔會得罪班的士佬架啦，死心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede8073c33050df9bbb4eb4fc43c302fd09a1e11","tid":2187572,"uid":8014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:58:33.000Z","msg":"餵豬一句唔like 呀<br />\n<br />\n比你2百萬民意反映咪一樣無鳩用"},{"pid":"351e2738d396fe12f722b8400161b2d8769716ee","tid":2187572,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:43:03.000Z","msg":"無可能架啦<br />\n<br />\n的士太多既得利益者  黑既佔左一大類<br />\n<br />\n黑專係幫政府做污糟野 你估政府會唔會俾你剝削黑利益"},{"pid":"6feb6458db28347bc8632d39670e56689a4c5468","tid":2187572,"uid":305602,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aec735c007a58cf367c441ca1290b6631def114d","tid":2187572,"uid":223868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T18:05:51.000Z","msg":"政府就係咁仆街 唔比你地舒服"},{"pid":"9da370c63eb250a80cff7a47015b2ed2afa3093e","tid":2187572,"uid":223868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T18:07:04.000Z","msg":"btw其實uber繼續而家咁有咩問題 佢都係走緊法律罅都係吹佢唔脹"},{"pid":"f4d326ca5a89ac2c4e58abbf126f4820ebd2d9a6","tid":2187572,"uid":592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"Uber 合法化<br />\n譚惠珠唔會嘈鳩你？"},{"pid":"c78a935da960a7d7d9cb1afe4240464c2494a1fb","tid":2187572,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9da370c63eb250a80cff7a47015b2ed2afa3093e","tid":2187572,"uid":223868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T18:07:04.000Z","msg":"btw其實uber繼續而家咁有咩問題 佢都係走緊法律罅都係吹佢唔脹"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T18:41:10.000Z","msg":"Uber司機成日比人放蛇捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091d18b3ab0e2a0b6f3e8af213b532d785909fdc","tid":2187572,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T18:52:11.000Z","msg":"On9 uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲對香港政府有期望<br />\n而且以為政府會聽民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3229e9ffbd13f5382c4a349ca8db9f2c88b71afd","tid":2187572,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T19:31:47.000Z","msg":"創科局最大貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9374bfe4d8d44ab1b6e0defd4244077db4ead57c","tid":2187572,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c78a935da960a7d7d9cb1afe4240464c2494a1fb","tid":2187572,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9da370c63eb250a80cff7a47015b2ed2afa3093e","tid":2187572,"uid":223868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09